\v 15 Xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Nˀai³-na¹ nca³tsˀi³ xi¹ncjin¹ ma³ ya⁴ ncˀa³jmi³ cao⁴ i⁴ son³ˀnte³.
\v 16 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ je² Espíritu Santo-le⁴ ca²ta³tsjoa¹jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-no³ xi³ tse³ nca³nˀion¹, jo³-sˀin² nca³ nˀion¹ tse³ cjoa⁴je³ya³-le⁴.
\v 17 Nta³ ca²ta³vˀe²jna³jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-no³ Cristo nca³ ma³cjain¹-no³. Vˀe³tsˀoa²³ nca³ nˀion¹ coi⁴yo³cao⁴³ nca³ nˀion¹tˀa³ coaon⁴³ cjoa⁴tjao²cha³,
\v 18 jme¹-ni³ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² sˀe⁴-si¹ni³no³ nca³nˀion¹ nca³ ña³qui³ nta³ coan⁴cho⁴ya³-si¹ni³no³ cao⁴ nca³tsˀi³ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ Cristo jo³ cji³ cjoa⁴tjao²cha³-le⁴ Cristo, jo³ cji³ te³ya³, jo³ cji³ nto³, jo³ cji³ na⁴nca⁴, jo³ cji³ ncˀa³.
\v 19 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² jcha⁴-nio¹³ je² cjoa⁴tjao²cha³-le⁴ Cristo, xi³ ña³qui³ fa³ˀa³ti¹tjon²-le⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³, jme¹-ni³ nca³ jtse¹jin³-si¹ni³no³ nca³yi³je³ xi³ tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹.
\v 20 Ni³na¹ nqui²sa⁴ to⁴tse³ ma³-le⁴ sˀin¹ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴ jo³ cji³ xi³ ni²je¹, jo³-sˀin² fa³ˀai³tsjen³-na¹, to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ je² nca³nˀion¹ xi³ si¹xa¹jin³-na¹.
\v 21 Je² ca²ta³vi³tjo³je³ya³ ya⁴jin³-le⁴ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴ Cristo xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Cristo Jesús, to⁴jo³ tjin¹ ni⁴čhjin³ nca³ntsjai² nca³ntsjai². Cˀoa⁴ ca²ta³ma³.
\c 4
\s1 Je² Espíritu Santo vˀe¹cjao²-na¹
\p 
\v 1 An³ xi³ ti²jna⁴ cjoa⁴ñˀain³ xi³ ti²jna⁴coa⁴ je² Nai³-na¹, vˀe³tsˀoa²³-no³ nca³ coi⁴mao³ jo³-sˀin² ma³chjen¹ je² xa¹ xi³ qui³no²cjoa⁴-no³,
\v 2 cao⁴ cjoa⁴yo⁴ma⁴ cjia³ta³con²³, cao⁴ cjoa⁴ntˀe¹, cao⁴ cjoa⁴tse³ta³con², Ti⁴cjain¹-lao⁴³ xi³nquio⁴³ nca³ tjao²chao³.
\v 3 Ti⁴xi¹ti¹ya³-lao⁴³ yao³-no³ nca³ to⁴jnco³ ti⁴yo³cjao³ nca³ nchˀan¹ ti³yo³, nca³ je² Espíritu Santo tsa³cˀe¹cjao³-no³.
\v 4 Jnco³ yao³ tjin¹. Jnco³ Espíritu Santo tjin¹, jo³-sˀin² nca³ cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ qui³no²cjoa⁴-no³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ jnco³ cjoa⁴cho³ya²cao⁴cjoa⁴ xi³ qui³sˀe³-no³ nca³ qui³no²cjoa⁴-no³.
\v 5 Jnco³ Nai³-na¹ tjin¹, jnco³ jo³-sˀin² nca³ ma³cjain¹-na¹, jnco³ cjoa⁴sa³te²nta¹,
\v 6 jnco³ Ni³na¹, cˀoa⁴ Nˀai³-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³, je² xi³ ti¹jna³ti¹tjon²-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³, xi³ ti¹jna³cao⁴ nca³tsˀi³, xi³ ti¹jna³jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³.
\v 7 To⁴nca³ nca³ jnco¹jncoa¹ tsa³cˀai²-na¹ cjoa⁴nta³ jo³-sˀin² choa⁴-le⁴ Cristo xi³ tsjoa¹cjoa⁴tjao²-na¹.
\v 8 Je² Ni³na¹ cˀoi⁴qui³tso²: Ncjin² ma³-ni³ xi³ tjio¹tˀa³nˀion¹ xi³ qui³cao⁴ cˀia⁴ nca³ qui³mi³ncˀa³, cˀoa⁴ qui³tsjoa³-le⁴ cjoa⁴tjao² cho⁴ta⁴son³ˀnte³.
\v 9 Xi³ qui³mi³ncˀa³, jo¹ tso²-ni³le⁴ tsa² tsi² ji³tjo³jen³ ya⁴ ˀnte³ xi³ nqui²sa⁴ na³nqui³ xi³ tsˀe⁴ son³ˀnte³.
\v 10 Je² xi³ ji³tjo³jen³, ti⁴je²-ni³ xi³ ja³ˀa³to³-sa³le⁴ ncˀa³jmi³ nca³ qui³mi³ncˀa³, jme¹-ni³ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² si⁴²jnco³si¹ni³-le⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴.
\v 11 Ti⁴je²-ni³ xi³ qui³tsjoa³-le⁴ cˀa³ nca³ pa²stro⁴ ma³, cˀoa⁴ xi³cˀa³ nca³ vˀe¹ma³ nchja⁴ya³, cˀoa⁴ xi³cˀa³ nca³ vˀe¹ma³son² nca³ tso²ya³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹, cˀoa⁴ xi³cˀa³ nca³ pastor ma³, cˀoa⁴ nca³ maestro ma³.
\v 12 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² coan³ jme¹-ni³ nca³ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ Cristo nta³ coa⁴tio⁴-si¹ni³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ xa¹-le⁴ nca³ si⁴²xa¹-le⁴ Ni³na¹. Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² je² yao³-le⁴ Cristo coin⁴ncˀa³.
\v 13 Sa³ˀnta³ nca³ cjoi³choa³² nca³ to⁴jnco³ coan⁴-nia¹ nca³tsˀia³² jo³-sˀin² coan⁴cjain¹-na¹, jo³-sˀin² jcha⁴xcoan³² je² ˀnti¹-le⁴ Ni³na¹, nca³ cjoe⁴ coan⁴nca³-na¹ jo³-ni³ tsa² jnco³ cho⁴ta⁴jchi¹nca³, jo³ sa³ˀnta³ cjoi³choa³² choa⁴ nca³ cˀoa⁴ coan⁴ cjoan³² jo³ cjoan³ Cristo.
\v 14 A³li² ti⁴cˀoa⁴ sˀian⁴²-nia³ jo³-ni³ tsa² ˀnti¹xti³ xi³ si¹cˀo¹fa³ya³ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-le⁴, xi³ jo³-ni³ tsa² ntjao⁴ xi³ tjen⁴ nca³ i⁴ nca³ jan¹, xi³ to⁴fi²tjen⁴nqui³-le⁴ xi³ to⁴cja⁴ˀai¹ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³, xi³ to⁴cjoa⁴ma²ña⁴-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴son³ˀnte³, xi³ vˀa³na⁴cha⁴ cao⁴ je² xi³ tsi² tsa² coi³ nta³ tjin¹, xi³ fi²cao⁴ tˀa³xin² jña³-le⁴ xi³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴.
\v 15 To⁴sa³ cjoin³tjen⁴nqui³-le⁴² xi³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ cao⁴ cjoa⁴tjao²cha³. Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² ca²ta³ma³jcha¹jin³-na¹ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ nca³ je² xi³ jcoa³² ma³, xi³ je² Cristo.
\v 16 Xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Cristo nca³yi³je³ yao³-le⁴ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² ma³yˀai³ ma³ncˀa³ cao⁴ cjoa⁴tjao²cha³, nca³ je³nta³ tjio¹cjao³ nca³qui³jnta² jña³ nca³ xco¹-le⁴. Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² tjin¹-le⁴ nca³nˀion¹ jo³-sˀin² nca³ nta³ si¹xa¹ jnco¹jnco¹ cˀa³ xi³ tsˀe⁴ yao³-le⁴.
\s1 Cristo si¹cho⁴tse⁴ya³-na¹
\p 
\v 17 Je²-vi⁴ xi³ cˀoa⁴xian³, cˀoa⁴ vˀe³ne²³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Nai³-na¹, nca³ tsi² tsa² ti⁴coi⁴ma³-nio³ jo³-ni³ xi³cˀa³ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ li² judío-jin², xi³ tjio¹ma³cao⁴ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-le⁴ xi³ tsi²jme³ chji¹-le⁴.
\v 18 To⁴njion² tjio¹ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-le⁴. Cjai¹nca³ to⁴tˀa³xin² tjio¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴vi³jna³chon³-le⁴ Ni³na¹ nca⁴ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² to⁴cjoa⁴njion² tjin¹-le⁴, cˀoa⁴ nca⁴ cjai¹nca³ xi¹jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-le⁴.
\v 19 Coan³scan³-ni³ nca³ je³qui³si³cha³jin³ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³nta³-le⁴, to⁴cˀoa⁴-sˀin² qui³sca³ni¹taon³ yao³-le⁴ nca³ to⁴cho⁴ta⁴cjoa⁴soa³ coan³. To⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ cjoa⁴xin²ta³con²-le⁴ cˀoa⁴qui³sˀin³ jo³ tjin¹ jco⁴ya³ cjoa⁴jnti¹.
\v 20 To⁴nca³ li²coi³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² qui³cho²tˀa³yao³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Cristo.
\v 21 A³ tsi² tsa³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ nca³ qui³no²ˀyao²³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Cristo, nca³ tsa³qui³yo³cao⁴³ nca³ qui³cho²tˀa³yao³ jo³-sˀin² nca³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ xi³ tjin¹ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Cristo.
\v 22 Chja⁴ˀa²xin²-lao⁴³ yao³-no³ je² ni⁴ma⁴-no³ xi³ jchi¹nca³ xi³ cjai¹nca³ to⁴coan³nca³-le⁴ cjoa⁴ xi³ chˀao³ tjin¹ jo³ tso² cjoa⁴tsjoa³-le⁴ yao³-no³ xi³ to⁴vˀa³na⁴cha⁴, jo³-sˀin² tsa³nquin¹cao⁴³ yao³-no³ nca³sˀa⁴.
\v 23 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² ca²ta³ma³cho⁴tse⁴ya³ jo³ tjin¹ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-no³.
\v 24 Chjoao¹³ je² ni⁴ma⁴-no³ xi³ cho⁴tse⁴, xi³ nco³ya³-le⁴ Ni³na¹ qui³sˀe³nta³-ni³ cao⁴ xi³ tjin¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ xi³ ña³qui³ tsje³.
\v 25 Coi³ nca³ qui³chja³ˀa²xion²³ cjoa⁴nti³so³, cho⁴va²cao⁴³ xi²nquio⁴³ xi³ cjoa⁴qui²xi, nca³ to⁴jnco³ tji¹cjao³ yao³-na¹ nca³tsˀia³².
\v 26 Nta³ tsa² ma³jti³-no³, a³li² je¹-jin² vi³jncho³. A³li² jti³-jin² ma³-no³ jo³ sa³ˀnta³ nca³ ca²ntjai² tsˀoi¹.
\v 27 Ni⁴ vˀai²ˀnte³-jin²lao⁴³ nai⁴².
\v 28 Je² xi³ qui³si³che¹, a³li² ti⁴si¹che¹-jin²ni³. To⁴sa³ ca²ta³si¹xa¹, cˀoa⁴-sˀin² ca²ta³si¹xa¹-ni³ ntsja³ xi³ nta³ tjin¹, jme¹-ni³ nca³ sˀe⁴-si¹ni³le⁴ xi³ tsjoa¹-le⁴ xi³ tsi²jme³ tjin¹-le⁴.
\v 29 Ni⁴to⁴jnco³-jin² en¹ xi³ chˀao³ tso² nˀo¹sje³-nio³ ntso⁴ˀvao³, to⁴je² en¹ xi³ nta³ tjin¹ xi³ coi⁴ncha³cao⁴, xi³ ma³chjen¹-le⁴, jme¹-ni³ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² tsjoa¹-si¹ni³le⁴ cjoa⁴nta³ je² xi³ nčhˀoe¹.
\v 30 A³li² cˀoa⁴-jin²sˀin² ni²va³-jin²lao⁴³ je² Espíritu Santo xi³ tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹, xi³ tsa³ca³sen¹choa⁴-no³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ cˀia⁴ ni⁴čhjin³ nca³ coan⁴chji¹ntjao²³.
\v 31 Nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴jnčha³, cjoa⁴jti³, cjoa⁴jti³cha³, xi³ nˀion¹ nchja⁴ti³, cao⁴ xi³ nchja⁴ˀaon³, ca²ta³tjo³xin²-no³, cao⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴tsˀen⁴.
\v 32 To⁴sa³ nta³ ti⁴cao⁴³ xi²nquio⁴³. Ca²ta³sˀe³-no³ cjoa⁴ma⁴ta³con². Ti⁴cha³tˀa³-lao⁴³ xi²nquio⁴³, jo³-sˀin² nca³ Ni³na¹ qui³si³cha³tˀa³-no³ nca³ ti³yo³cao⁴³ Cristo.
\c 5
\s1 Coi⁴ma³² jo³-ni³ tsa² ˀnti¹-le⁴ Ni³na¹ xi³ i³sen³-le⁴
\p 
\v 1 Chjen²nqui³-lao⁴³ Ni³na¹, jo³-ni³ tsa² ˀnti¹ xi³ cjai¹nca³ tjao²cha³.
\v 2 Cao⁴ cjoa⁴tjao²cha³ ti⁴ma³cao⁴³ xi²nquio⁴³, jo³-sˀin² Cristo coan³tsjoa³que³-na¹, qui³tsjoa³ntjai²-na¹ yao³-le⁴, jo³-ni³ jnco³ cjoa⁴tjao², cˀoa⁴ jo³-ni³ xi³ qui³tsˀai²ntjai²-na¹ xi³ na³sca¹ njen⁴ nqui³xcon⁴ Ni³na¹.
\v 3 A³li² ni²cˀa³xqui⁴jin³-jion²³ xi²nquio⁴³ ni⁴ˀi⁴tse¹-jin² cjoa⁴cha³jnqui³, ni⁴ nca³yi³je³ xi³ nˀion¹ chˀao³ tjin¹, ni⁴ cjoa⁴xin²ta³con²-jin². Je² cjoa⁴-vi⁴ li²coi³ ntia⁴² squen¹-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ Cristo.
\v 4 Ni⁴ je²-jin² en¹tsˀen⁴ no²cjoao⁴³, ni⁴ en¹chi⁴con¹-jin², ni⁴ en¹ntsjen¹ˀa³-jin², xi³ tsi² tsa² va³quin²-no³, to⁴sa³ tˀao²³ cjoa⁴nta³.
\v 5 Je³ˀyao³ je²-vi⁴, nca³ ni⁴jnco³-jin² cho⁴ta⁴cha³jnqui³, ni⁴jnco³-jin² xi³ cjoa⁴jnti¹ tjio¹ma³sˀin¹, ni⁴jnco³-jin² xi³ xin²con³, xi³ ma³nco¹son² xi³ xco¹son² ve³xcon¹, ni⁴jnco³-jin² tjin¹-le⁴ ˀnte³ ya⁴ cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³-le⁴ Cristo cao⁴ Ni³na¹.
\v 6 Ni⁴to⁴ˀya³-jin² xi³ ca²ta³vˀa³na⁴cha⁴-no³ cao⁴ xi³ to⁴xquia⁴ en¹. Xi³ to⁴coi³ cjoa⁴-vi⁴ nčhoa¹ne²-le⁴ cjoa⁴jti³-le⁴ Ni³na¹ je² cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ xi¹jin³.
\v 7 A³li² ya⁴-jin² ña³tjen⁴ mai¹cao⁴³ nca³ je².
\v 8 Nca³sˀa⁴ njion² nio¹³, to⁴nca³ ntˀai⁴-vi⁴ntai⁴ je³ˀi³saon³ nca³ ti³yo³cao⁴³ je² Nai³-na¹. Ti⁴mao³ jo³-ni³ tsa² ˀnti¹-le⁴ xi³ i³sen³-le⁴.
\v 9 (Je² Espíritu Santo tsjoa¹ntje⁴jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-na¹ je² xi³ cjoa⁴nta³, xi³ tjin¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴, cˀoa⁴ je² xi³ ña³qui³ cˀoa⁴tjin¹.)
\v 10 Cho¹tˀao³ je² xi³ sa³sen¹con³ Nai³-na¹.
\v 11 A³li² cˀoa⁴-jin²sˀin² nˀiaon²³ je² xa¹ xi³ tsi² coan⁴ntje⁴-no³, xi³ to⁴tsˀe⁴ cjoa⁴njion², to⁴sa³ ta⁴co²son²tsaon⁴³.
\v 12 Cjai¹nca³ to⁴chˀao³ tjin¹, nta³ tsa² to⁴coi⁴no²cjoao⁴³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ je² xi³ to⁴cjoa⁴ˀma³ sˀin¹.
\v 13 Nca³yi³je³ je² cjoa⁴ xi³ va³tio²son²tsen³, cˀoa⁴-sˀin² sa³tio²son²tsen³ cao⁴ lˀi¹. Je² nca³yi³je³ xi³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² va³tio²son²tsen³, i³sen³ jo³-ni³ tsa² lˀi¹.
\v 14 Xi³ coi³ cˀoi⁴tso²: Ti⁴cja³ˀa¹-lai⁴ yao³-li⁴, ji³ xi³ ti³so³jna³fai³. Ti²so⁴tjen⁴jin³-lai⁴ cˀen³, cˀoa⁴-sˀin² si⁴²ˀi³sen³-li² Cristo.
\v 15 Cho¹tsaon³, tso²cˀoa⁴, nca³ qui²xi⁴ ti⁴mao³, a³li² jo³-ni³ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ tsin²-le⁴ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-jin², to⁴nca³ jo³-ni³ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ tjin¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³.
\v 16 A³li² ni⁴čhjin³-jin² ni²cha³-lao⁴³ yao³-no³, nca³ je² ni⁴čhjin³ cjai¹nca³ to⁴chˀao³ chon³.
\v 17 Xi³ coi³, a³li² chi⁴con¹-jin² mao³, to⁴nca³ ca²ta³ma³cho⁴ya³-no³ jo³-sˀin² nca³ me³-le⁴ Nai³-na¹.
\v 18 A³li² yao³-no³jin² ni²chˀi⁴-nio³ vino, nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² si¹qui³xo²ya³-ni³ cjoa⁴, to⁴nca³ ca²ta³tse³jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-no³ je² Espíritu Santo.
\v 19 Chja⁴cao⁴³ xi²nquio⁴³ je² en¹-le⁴ Ni³na¹ xi³ coi⁴jntao¹³, ti⁴jnta¹-lao⁴³ je² xi³ vˀa³sje³je³ya³ Ni³na¹, ti⁴jntao¹³ ja⁴jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-no³. Ti⁴jnta¹-lao⁴³, cˀoa⁴ chˀa⁴sje³je³yao³ je² Nai³-na¹ ja⁴jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-no³.
\v 20 Nca³ntsjai² nca³yi³je³ tˀai²-lao⁴³ cjoa⁴nta³ Ni³na¹ Nˀai³-na¹ xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ jan³ˀain¹-le⁴ Nai³-na¹ Jesucristo.
\s1 Na³nqui³ coi⁴yo³-le⁴² xi²nquia⁴²
\p 
\v 21 Na³nqui³ ti⁴yo³-lao⁴³ xi²nquio⁴³ nca³ jcon³ chao³ Ni³na¹.
\v 22 Je² ya¹nchjin¹ na³nqui³ ca²ta³va³tio²-le⁴ xˀin⁴-le⁴, jo³-sˀin² nca³ na³nqui³ tjio¹-le⁴ Nai³-na¹.
\v 23 Je² xˀin⁴-ve⁴ nca³jco⁴-le⁴ chjon⁴²-le⁴, jo³-sˀin² nca³ Cristo nca³jco⁴-le⁴ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴. Je² xi³ vˀa³sje³ntjai² na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴ xi³ ti⁴je²-ni³ yao³-le⁴.
\v 24 Jo³-sˀin² nca³ je² na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴ Cristo na³nqui³ tjio¹-le⁴ Cristo, cˀoa⁴-ti⁴sˀin²ni³ nca³ je² ya¹nchjin¹ na³nqui³ tjio¹-le⁴ xˀin⁴-le⁴ nca³yi³je³.
\v 25 Jon² xi³ xˀion⁴³, tsjoa³cha³ ca²ta³mao³ ya¹nchjin¹-no³, jo³-sˀin² nca³ Cristo coan³tsjoa³que³ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴, cˀoa⁴ qui³tsjoa³ntjai² yao³-le⁴ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴,
\v 26 jme¹-ni³ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² Cristo tsa³cˀe¹jna³tjao²-si¹ni³ cˀoa⁴ qui³si³tsje³-si¹ni³ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴, jo³-ni³ tsa² cao⁴ na³nta¹ xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ en¹-le⁴,
\v 27 jme¹-ni³ nca³ ti⁴je²-ni³ si⁴²ca³sen¹ va³sen³-si¹ni³le⁴ yao³-le⁴ jnco³ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹ xi³ tsˀe⁴ xi³ cjai¹nca³ to⁴je³ya³, xi³ tsi² tsa² coi³ je² tjin¹-le⁴, xi³ tsi² tsa² yo¹ cjoan³, ni⁴to⁴cˀoa⁴cjoan³ cˀoa⁴ma³-jin², jme¹-ni³ nca³ to⁴ña³qui³ tsje³ coan⁴-si¹ni³ nca³ tsi²jme³ je¹ sˀe⁴-le⁴.
\v 28 Cˀoa⁴-ti⁴sˀin² xi³ xˀin⁴ tsjoa³que³ ca²ta³ma³ ya¹nchjin¹-le⁴, jo³-ni³ tsa² ti⁴tsˀe⁴-ni³ yao³. Je² xi³ tsjoa³que³ chjon⁴²-le⁴, ti⁴je²-ni³ yao³-le⁴ xi³ tsjoa³que³.
\v 29 Ni⁴jnco³-jin² xi³ ti⁴je² taon³ ve³-ni³ yao³-le⁴. To⁴cˀoa⁴sˀin² si¹jcha¹, cˀoa⁴ tjao²-le⁴, jo³-ni³ tsa² Cristo si¹jcha¹, cˀoa⁴ tjao²-le⁴ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-le⁴.
\v 30 Nca³ ña¹ tjio¹cjao³-nia¹ yao³-le⁴ cao⁴ ni³nta³-le⁴.
